#. Tag: screen
#: x11.xml:316
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&prompt.sudo;zypper addrepo --refresh https://download.nvidia.com/opensuse/"
"leap/15.&product-sp; nvidia"
msgstr ""
"&prompt.sudo;zypper addrepo --refresh https://download.nvidia.com/opensuse/"
"leap/15.&product-sp; nvidia"

